  <entry>
    <title>How to build debian packages using Docker</title>
    <link href="https://blog.youya.org/2015/09/24/how-to-build-debian-packages-using-docker/"/>
    <id>https://blog.youya.org/2015/09/24/how-to-build-debian-packages-using-docker/</id>
    <published>2015-09-24T14:26:53.000Z</published>
    <updated>2016-04-04T11:08:41.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;This article shows how to build debian packages using Docker. The process is to build a debian package during build a Docker image and extract the debian package while creating the Docker container.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;a id=&quot;more&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;Preparation&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#Preparation&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;Preparation&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Preparation&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Docker 1.6.0&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Package name: mesos&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Source code: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/mesos&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/mesos&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;debian directory: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/chenzhiwei/linux/tree/master/debian/debian&quot;&gt;https://github.com/chenzhiwei/linux/tree/master/debian/debian&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;Dockerfile&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#Dockerfile&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;Dockerfile&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Dockerfile&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight dockerfile&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; ubuntu:&lt;span class=&quot;number&quot;&gt;14.04&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;comment&quot;&gt;# Install enssential packages for Mesos&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;RUN&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;apt-get update &amp;amp;&amp;amp; apt-get -y install \&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;    autoconf \&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;    build-essential \&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;    debhelper \&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;    git \&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;    libapr1-dev \&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;    libcurl4-nss-dev \&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;    libsasl2-dev \&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;    libsvn-dev \&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;    libtool \&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;    maven \&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;    openjdk-7-jdk \&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;    python-boto \&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;    python-dev&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;comment&quot;&gt;# Checkout Mesos code&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;RUN&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;git &lt;span class=&quot;built_in&quot;&gt;clone&lt;/span&gt; https://github.com/apache/mesos /mesos&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;comment&quot;&gt;# Copy debian directory to  mesos source directory&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;COPY&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;debian /mesos/debian&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;comment&quot;&gt;# Build Mesos debian package&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;RUN&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;built_in&quot;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; /mesos &amp;amp;&amp;amp; dpkg-buildpackage -us -uc&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;Building&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#Building&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;Building&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Building&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Before building the package, you should make sure the directory structure is like following:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight gherkin&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;|&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;-- ./debian&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;|&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;   &lt;/span&gt;|&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;-- ./debian/changelog&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;|&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;   &lt;/span&gt;|&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;-- ./debian/compat&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;|&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;   &lt;/span&gt;|&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;-- ./debian/control&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;|&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;   &lt;/span&gt;|&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;-- ./debian/copyright&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;|&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;   `-- ./debian/rules&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;`-- ./Dockerfile&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run build Docker image command&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight armasm&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;symbol&quot;&gt;docker&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;build &lt;/span&gt;-t mesos:&lt;span class=&quot;number&quot;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span class=&quot;number&quot;&gt;25&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span class=&quot;number&quot;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; .&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Check the Docker images after the build command&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight nginx&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;attribute&quot;&gt;docker&lt;/span&gt; images&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;Extract-the-debian-package&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#Extract-the-debian-package&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;Extract the debian package&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Extract the debian package&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight groovy&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;docker run --rm -v &lt;span class=&quot;regexp&quot;&gt;/tmp:/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;data:&lt;/span&gt;rw &lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;mesos:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;number&quot;&gt;0.25&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;number&quot;&gt;.0&lt;/span&gt; sh -c &lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&#39;cp /mesos-*.deb /data&#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will see a mesos debian package in your &lt;code&gt;/tmp&lt;/code&gt; directory.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;Remove-the-Docker-images&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#Remove-the-Docker-images&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;Remove the Docker images&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Remove the Docker images&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can choose whether to remove the &lt;code&gt;mesos:0.25.0&lt;/code&gt; Docker image or not.&lt;/p&gt;
</content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;This article shows how to build debian packages using Docker. The process is to build a debian package during build a Docker image and extract the debian package while creating the Docker container.&lt;/p&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
    
